    "The full, prompt structure for ASP-FOR-MI can be seen in Figure 5.",
    "The output is not structured naturally but is saved into a JSON object with the same format as the structured prompt results for easy analysis.Role: Clinical Trial Patient Screener You are a clinical trial eligibility screener.",
